short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get Access to coupon deals on the Internet

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Override the new tab page with Best Daily Coupons to get online coupons from your new tab page. 
Override the new tab page with our Best Daily Coupons Chrome Plugin. You can get online coupons directly on your new tab page.

This extension configures your New Tab page to Best Daily Coupons to provide this content and features described within your New Tab page.

Please read carefully: By clicking the “Free+ Add to Chrome” button in the top right hand corner above and installing the Best Daily Coupons Tab extension, you agree to install this application, and you agree to the End User License Agreement and the Privacy Policy and to receiving any future updates and upgrades. The application communicates with our servers to deliver its functionality and record usage metrics. You can uninstall the program at any time.
